Author: Nicolas Dodelier

Includes wiiuse v0.12 by Michael Laforest. http://wiiuse.net/

In order to compile luawie, these packages are required:
make gcc liblua5.1-dev libbluetooth-dev libxtst-dev

Then:
$ make
$ ./luawie3 script/tests/wiimote.lua

Hold A + B (on your wiimote) to quit this test.

The scripts/ folder contains file for playing frets on fire
with a wii guitar, playing snes games using zsnes and a
classic controller, etc...
